name: NFTSwaps
additional_notices: Kindly be aware that liquidity provided in Automated Market Maker platforms (eg. Uniswap, Sushiswap, Balancer) can be removed (also known as rug pulling), resulting in a collapse of available liquidity. Please exercise caution when trading! This notice is NOT directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder for our users.

description.en: NFTSwaps is a product of Blockchain4Africa Limited. The company is created to provide e-commerce services, Internet Marketing, ICT, and blockchain-based services. The Blockchain4africa team has been active in multiple projects in the Blockchain industry and have extensive experience with DAPP development. Our team is composed of multiple blockchain experts from all around the world focused and dedicated to bringing you a transparent and provably fair blockchain-based decentralized platform.
